main_body:
As regards the support provided for in Article 1, the Member States shall communicate to the Commission:
(a) without delay and no later than 31 March 2010, a description of the objective criteria used to determine the methods for granting support and the provisions taken to avoid distortion of the market;
(b) no later than 30 August 2010, the total amounts of aid paid and the number and type of beneficiaries.
